8 Highway 82 to U.S. Highway 271; from U.S. Highway 271 to State
9 Highway 1; and from State Highway 1 and ending at the intersection
10 of State Highway 1 and U.S. Highway 259.
11 B. The Department of Transportation shall erect informational
12 highway signage designed or approved by the Oklahoma Tourism and
13 Recreation Department to direct visitors to sites of significant
14 interest along the True Grit Trail, including:
15 1. The city of Sallisaw;
16 2. The town of Spiro;
17 3. The town of Bokoshe;
18 4. The town of McCurtain;
19 5. The town of Kinta;
